Subject: Re: [T2] 1700 Cylinder Head Mystery Holes

Sounds like a true "head leak" the stock engines had aluminum, head gaskets,
they blow, and do this nasty deed, there was a VW bulletin that made the
head gaskets a thing of the past, we do not use them, and have no head leak
problems..
Jake Raby
Raby's Aircooled Technology
